        "contents": "function largestOfAll(arr) {\r\n  return arr.map(subArr => Math.max.apply(null, subArr));\r\n}\r\n\r\nlargestOfAll([\r\n  [4, 5, 1, 3],\r\n  [13, 27, 18, 26],\r\n  [32, 35, 37, 39],\r\n  [1000, 1001, 857, 1]\r\n]);",
