    {
      "text": "<p><code>largestOfAll([[4, 5, 1, 3], [13, 27, 18, 26], [32, 35, 37, 39], [1000, 1001, 857, 1]])</code> Trebalo bi da vrati red podataka.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.isArray(\r\n  largestOfAll([\r\n    [4, 5, 1, 3],\r\n    [13, 27, 18, 26],\r\n    [32, 35, 37, 39],\r\n    [1000, 1001, 857, 1]\r\n  ])\r\n);"
